Starring: Barry Sloane, Kyle Schmid, Juan Pablo Raba, Walton GogginsGenre: DramaPremier date: January 18Six is an action packed mini-series which chronicles the lives of the members of SEAL Team Six; a special counter-terrorism unit in the U.S. Armed Forces. Former Six troop leader Rip Target has been captured by the terrorist group Boko Haram in Nigeria and his old teammates are sent to rescue him before the enemy manages to extract sensitive information. The team is forced to relive some of their worst memories from a previous mission Afghanistan, testing friendships and loyalty. The show exposes all the realness of dark side of being a soldier, much like The Secret Soldiers of Benghazi, but also manages to show the &lsquo;regular suburbia husband&rsquo; side of a soldier.